Queens Park Rangers have agreed a £4.78million deal in principle for Ajax striker Kolbeinn Sigthorsson.

Harry Redknapp knows he needs to bolster his squad ahead of next season following their promotion from the Championship.

And the Loftus Road club have a agreed a fee with the Dutch club for the Iceland forward.

